[[瓊·傑特|瓊·傑特]]在和''[[The_Runaways|The Runaways]]''于英国巡回演出时 <ref name="Cover song">[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-29568083 "Ten hits you may not know were cover versions"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-29568083 |date=20170911191347 }}. BBC News. Retrieved 14 October 2014</ref> 在英国电视剧《''[[Arrows_(电视剧)|Arrows]]''》中看见乐队''Arrows''表演本歌曲 <ref name="Outsight Radio Hours interview"/> 她于1979年和[[性手槍|性手槍]]的两位成员[[史蒂夫·琼斯_(歌手)|史蒂夫·琼斯]]和[[保羅·庫克|保羅·庫克]]录制了本歌曲。1979年，歌曲以黑胶的形式第一次发行。1981年，傑特和她的乐队''The Blackhearts''重新灌录了歌曲。这一次录制的版本成功获得美国[[告示牌百强单曲榜|告示牌百强单曲榜]]冠军7周。<ref>[[Joel_Whitburn|Whitburn, Joel]] (2004). ''The Billboard Book of Top 40 Hits'', 8th Edition (Billboard Publications), page 322.</ref> 并被[[美国唱片业协会|美国唱片业协会]]认证为白金唱片，同时为收录本单曲的专辑《''[[I_Love_Rock_'n'_Roll_(专辑)|I Love Rock 'n' Roll]]''》增加了近200万销量，并使专辑获得[[告示牌二百强专辑榜|告示牌二百强专辑榜]]亚军。瓊·傑特翻唱的版本在《[[滾石雜誌|滚石]]》百大百大单曲榜中排行第89。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/news/coverstory/20947527/page/37 |title=''Rolling Stone'' - The 100 Greatest Guitar Songs of All Time |accessdate=2008年5月30日 |deadurl=bot: unknown |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080530224818/http://www.rollingstone.com/news/coverstory/20947527/page/37 |archivedate=2008年5月30日 |df= }}. Retrieved 2011-01-24. "With the first primal power chord, Jett obliterated her image as a teenage girl-group novelty in The Runaways. The squealing riffs matched her new leather-clad tough-girl image and made her case as one of the fiercest female guitarists of all time."</ref>

